<p>My name is Alexa and I have been a student at Avada Dance for two years.</p>
<p> I never danced before I joined Avada Dance. I was always shy and insecure about my body and my abilities. I wanted to try something new and challenge myself, so I signed up for a beginner class at Avada Dance. </p>
